data.description: Location location location!!! This 4 bed 2 bath home in central Crestview is a must see. Your new home features a great location with easy access to your local bases, white sandy beachs, shopping, and doctors to name a few. To top things off your new home features a large .37 acre lot that backs to a wooded area for increased privacy making the covered back deck your own personal retreat. Inside you will be greeted with an open concept design with high cathedral ceilings in the main living areas, decoratice ledges, and a split bedroom floor plan for extra privacy from kids and guest after a long day of work to name a few. This home won't last long call to schedule your private viewing today!
